ThirdParty: ReadMe

ThirdParty contains projects for tools and libraries that do not belong in CocoaDocs, and for which we have source code.
Projects written and Cocoa and needed to build products are eligible for CocoaDocs, and should be stored there instead.

This project contains a file current_versions.html That contains minimal information for each project,
as well as revision information that can be used to help keep our tools and libraries up-to-date.
